{"id": 1897, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得年轻人哪些被指责为“太自我/任性”的事其实没毛病？", "description": "实际上是人们对自我意识的觉醒有成见吧？", "record_count": 6224, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170910222242HxbgNT1OFP2JqMp3.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-09-11T03:00:18Z", "options": [{"id": 234752, "content": "大家好像都跟结婚杠上了，这是受了多大的刺激啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 126152}, {"id": 234753, "content": "你做了就做了呗，管他呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149075}, {"id": 235009, "content": "违心说假话", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 971371}, {"id": 234754, "content": "  沉迷于挣钱日渐消瘦，然后攒点钱后出去浪迹天涯寻找自己喜爱的事～", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1129776}, {"id": 234755, "content": "我想趁着年轻去拼搏 即使辛苦也想看看不一样的世界 。长辈会说幼稚 应该考个公务员稳定下来。", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 581967}, {"id": 234756, "content": "不依赖婚姻，期待自己能够有丝分裂", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1129784}, {"id": 235012, "content": "不知以为知 少知而不求知，自以为是", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 915698}, {"id": 234757, "content": "出柜", "image": null, "praise_count": 172, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1078715}, {"id": 234758, "content": "26岁不结婚", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 949271}, {"id": 235014, "content": "爱自由", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1096651}, {"id": 234759, "content": "性格直", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1129808}, {"id": 234760, "content": "我周末好不容易有时间不上班想休息休息 我在被窝里怎么就成不干正事了", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1129816}, {"id": 235528, "content": "不化妆，不穿高跟鞋，就是不“精致”了吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680675}, {"id": 234761, "content": "我们辛辛苦苦赚钱，你怎么不为我们想想", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1119666}, {"id": 234762, "content": "不听话", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1129821}, {"id": 234765, "content": "天天睡到自然醒.", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136629}, {"id": 234766, "content": "被家里人催婚", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1126525}, {"id": 234767, "content": "我未来不打算将赚到的钱投资到房产上，只是觉得租个够生活的房子住就好，却被认为是不成熟", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1215933}, {"id": 234768, "content": "22岁了，还不结婚？昨晚我姨，我妈说的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1126525}, {"id": 234770, "content": "我只是想过自己想要的生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1129839}, {"id": 234771, "content": "不喜欢圆滑世故 会为了亲爱的朋友们忍耐 但是对于保质期短的同事朋友 会把他们都屏蔽 不想强颜欢笑 只想让自己活得开心点", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814266}, {"id": 236051, "content": "为了谈恋爱而谈恋爱 没有达到经济实力绝不生孩子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 923358}, {"id": 234772, "content": "追女生，总以为自己会成功", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1100775}, {"id": 235028, "content": "指责很多都是嫉妒", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1130739}, {"id": 234773, "content": "不用微信朋友圈怎么了", "image": null, "praise_count": 62, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1115687}, {"id": 237845, "content": "不会享受生活，大部分时间都生活在网络空间，对身边的事物不闻不问……", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1140413}, {"id": 234774, "content": "我自己凭本事拿的奖学金，为啥天天追着我要吃饭？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1014450}, {"id": 236055, "content": "不结婚怎么了，不生孩子怎么了，人就活一次，当然要自己选择想要的生活，不需要在乎别人怎么说", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1133610}, {"id": 234777, "content": "做自己喜欢的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1129852}, {"id": 234778, "content": "不接收职场潜规则", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1257695}, {"id": 235546, "content": "说那么多干吗？一个字：干就完了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 927525}, {"id": 234779, "content": "同性恋没有孩子的，你们家要绝后了。\n我支持同性恋，可惜你们家要绝后了。\n\nemmmm，一个属于自己血脉的后代就那么重要？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 435368}, {"id": 234780, "content": "我只是想活的开心点", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688589}, {"id": 234781, "content": "对于\"家\"的概念不同，不要拿\"常回家看看\"套路别人了好么……", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 997563}, {"id": 234784, "content": "和深爱的人结婚，有错吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 537020}, {"id": 235040, "content": "活出自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 971409}, {"id": 235296, "content": "不想被工作填满生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1131551}, {"id": 234786, "content": "到了所谓的适婚年龄仍然想保持单身", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1129892}, {"id": 234787, "content": "随心所欲的活着", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1130651}, {"id": 235555, "content": "花钱买自己喜欢的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1131215}, {"id": 234788, "content": "有太多的不喜欢不愿意不想，不喜欢客套社交，不愿意被逼婚，不想被限制，我认为这没毛病\n因为除此之外我们还有很多喜欢愿意和想", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1129782}, {"id": 235045, "content": "我没人爱？\n只是我不愿意爱他们罢了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1130766}, {"id": 235301, "content": "自己赚的钱，买一些游戏的皮肤角色，怎么就挥霍无度了？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1131583}, {"id": 235046, "content": "人生不需要那么紧赶慢赶\n未知的才是有趣的", "image": "img/option/option/20170912193259c0i8syWHp3t2fePw.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1130766}, {"id": 235302, "content": "胸无大志，就愿做一平常人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1113262}, {"id": 234791, "content": "不结婚", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1125117}, {"id": 235047, "content": "最有骨气的表达方式\n               -\n       什么都不做", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1130766}, {"id": 234792, "content": "阅历真的不够", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 733028}, {"id": 235048, "content": "最有骨气的表达方式\n什么都不做", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1130766}, {"id": 234795, "content": "从来不会圆滑世故随波逐流", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 848137}]}